# See https://help.github.com/articles/ignoring-files/ for more about ignoring files.

# dependencies and build output
**/node_modules/
**/.next/
**/out/
**/coverage/
**/build/
**/.vercel/
**/*.tsbuildinfo

# Python caches and virtualenvs
.venv/
**/.venv/
**/__pycache__/
**/*.py[cod]
**/*.pyo
**/next-env.d.ts

# package manager metadata
/.pnp
.pnp.*
.yarn/*
!.yarn/patches
!.yarn/plugins
!.yarn/releases
!.yarn/versions

# misc
.DS_Store
*.pem

# debug
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
.pnpm-debug.log*

# env files (can opt-in for committing if needed)
.env*
!.env.local.example
